## Key Functions in rhoai-toolkit.sh

### Helper Functions
```bash
print_banner()                      # Display main banner
print_header(text)                  # Section header
print_step(text)                    # Step indicator
print_success(text)                 # Success message
print_error(text)                   # Error message
print_warning(text)                 # Warning message
print_info(text)                    # Info message
```

### CSR Approval
```bash
approve_pending_csrs()              # Approve Certificate Signing Requests
```

### Kubeconfig Management
```bash
configure_kubeconfig_menu()         # Interactive kubeconfig setup
```

### GPU Management
```bash
show_gpu_status()                   # Display GPU node status
run_nvidia_smi()                    # Run nvidia-smi on GPU node
uncordon_gpu_nodes()                # Re-enable scheduling
downgrade_gpu_operator()            # Downgrade to v24.6
show_clusterpolicy_status()         # Show ClusterPolicy
create_clusterpolicy()              # Create/apply ClusterPolicy
delete_clusterpolicy()              # Delete ClusterPolicy
```

### Model Management
```bash
deploy_model_menu()                 # Model deployment submenu
add_model_to_playground()           # Add to GenAI Studio
create_hardware_profile_menu()      # Hardware profile creation
quick_gpu_profile_setup()           # Pre-configured profiles
```

### MaaS & LlamaStack
```bash
setup_maas_menu()                   # MaaS setup (version-aware)
setup_llamastack_menu()             # LlamaStack setup
enable_llamastack_operator()        # Enable in DSC
```

### Feature Store
```bash
feast_submenu()                     # Feast management menu
run_feast_apply()                   # Execute feast apply
run_feast_materialize()             # Execute feast materialize
```

### Demos
```bash
deploy_open_webui()                 # Deploy Open WebUI
deploy_guidellm()                   # Deploy GuideLLM
deploy_llamastack_demo()            # Deploy LlamaStack demo
```

### Troubleshooting
```bash
fix_gpu_cuda_compatibility()        # Downgrade GPU operator
check_gpu_operator_status()         # Show operator status
restart_failed_model_pods()         # Restart stuck pods
restart_rhoai_controllers()         # Restart controllers
check_all_operator_status()         # Show all operators
```

### Quick Start Wizard
```bash
quick_start_wizard()                # Guided post-install workflow
```

### Day 2 Operations
```bash
day2_operations_menu()              # Day 2 tasks menu
```
